&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/post/2021-zambia-social-media-blocks-amid-elections/#blocking-of-whatsapp"&gt;Blocking of WhatsApp&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/post/2021-zambia-social-media-blocks-amid-elections/#blocking-of-twitter-and-facebook"&gt;Blocking of Twitter and Facebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
